@startuml ProveoUsage
!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/proveo-ca/identity/refs/heads/main/proveo.iuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

left to right direction

title Proveo Command Entrypoints and Component Usage

actor "Consumer" as Consumer
actor "Maintainer" as Maintainer

package "Consumer Entrypoint\napps/cli/public/images/bin" as ConsumerEntrypoint {
  component "proveo" as ConsumerCli <<app>>
  component "help\nlist\nrun <target>\nuninstall" as ConsumerCommands <<commands>>
  component "help.sh\nuninstall.sh" as ConsumerScripts <<script>>
}

package "Maintainer Entrypoint\nmise + lib/" as MaintainerEntrypoint {
  component "mise run <task>\nlib/*.sh helpers" as MaintainerCli <<internal>>
  component "build <target>\ntest-defs <target>\ndebug <target>\ndeploy <target>" as MaintainerCommands <<commands>>
}

package "Definition-Local Entrypoints\ndefs/<target>/" as DefinitionEntrypoints {
  component "build.sh\nrun.sh\ntest.sh / tests/\ndebug.sh" as DefinitionCommands <<script>>
}

package "Definitions and Defaults\ndefs/" as Definitions {
  component "Dockerfile*\nentrypoint.sh / start scripts" as DefinitionRuntime <<definition>>
  component "sample configs\ndefault agents\ndefinition tests" as DefinitionAssets <<asset>>
}

package "Monorepo Discovery" as Monorepo {
  component "git repo root\npnpm-workspace.yaml\nscope picker" as ScopeSelection <<logic>>
}

package "Egress Layer (claudecode run/debug)\ndefs/lib/egress.sh" as Egress {
  component "modes\nbroker|proxy|firewall" as EgressModes <<logic>>
  component "--local-model NAME\n(Ollama sidecar)" as EgressLocal <<logic>>
  component "provider allowlist\nauto-detected from API key" as EgressProvider <<logic>>
  component "Squid + mitmproxy + ollama sidecars\nreports/egress/<session>/report" as EgressSidecars <<runtime>>
}

package "Runtime and Artifacts" as Runtime {
  component "Docker CLI" as DockerCli <<runtime>>
  component "local images\nproveo/*" as LocalImages <<image>>
  component "remote registry\nproveo/*" as Registry <<external>>
  component "selected workspace\nreports / sessions / config dirs" as RuntimeMounts <<storage>>
}

Consumer --> ConsumerEntrypoint : installed usage
Maintainer --> MaintainerEntrypoint : repo-local wrapper
Maintainer --> DefinitionEntrypoints : direct deterministic commands

ConsumerEntrypoint --> Runtime : run uses Docker and images
ConsumerEntrypoint --> Monorepo : run selects workspace scope
ConsumerEntrypoint --> ConsumerScripts : help and uninstall delegate here

MaintainerEntrypoint --> DefinitionEntrypoints : build, test, run, debug delegate where possible
MaintainerEntrypoint --> Definitions : build/test fallback and target metadata
MaintainerEntrypoint --> Runtime : deploy pushes images; run/debug use images and mounts
MaintainerEntrypoint --> Monorepo : run/debug select workspace scope
MaintainerEntrypoint --> ConsumerScripts : uninstall delegates here

DefinitionEntrypoints --> Definitions : scripts consume definition files and defaults
DefinitionEntrypoints --> Runtime : build/run/test/debug use Docker, images, and mounts

Definitions --> Runtime : produces proveo/* images
Monorepo --> Runtime : resolves selected workspace mount

ConsumerEntrypoint ..> Egress : run claudecode --egress-mode
MaintainerEntrypoint --> Egress : run/debug claudecode --egress-mode
DefinitionEntrypoints --> Egress : defs/claudecode/run.sh sources egress.sh
Egress --> Runtime : sidecars, mounts, and egress report
EgressModes --> EgressSidecars
EgressLocal --> EgressSidecars
EgressProvider --> EgressSidecars

note right of ConsumerEntrypoint
Consumer commands:
- help: prints packaged help
- list: prints packaged target list
- run: pulls/runs proveo/* images
- uninstall: runs packaged uninstall script
end note

note right of MaintainerEntrypoint
Maintainer commands:
- help/list: embedded command metadata
- build/test/run/debug: use defs/<target>/ scripts
- deploy: pushes a tagged local image
- uninstall: reuses consumer lifecycle script
end note

note bottom of Definitions
Reusable agent definitions currently live as
definition defaults. A future packages/subagents
boundary can feed these defaults into CLIs/images.
end note

note bottom of Egress
claudecode run/debug can wrap the agent in a network
egress layer (defs/lib/egress.sh):
- open: direct bridge (default)
- proxy: Squid enforcement (HTTP/HTTPS only, non-web blocked)
- firewall: mitmproxy TLS inspection upstream of Squid
Provider egress is auto-pinned to the API key present;
web reads stay open. --local-model adds an Ollama
sidecar. Every run writes an egress report.
See claudecode-egress-topology.puml.
end note

@enduml
